snippet.title: Mulaka - Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into northern Mexico's most breathtaking landscape to experience the true life of a Sukurúame. Mulaka is a 3D action-adventure game based on the Rarámuri indigenous culture that explores the lore of these legendary people!

Coming 2017 to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 & PC!

Learn more at www.lienzo.mx/mulaka
